examples.en: No one likes to be suddenly awakened.
We were rudely awakened by the storm.
He was awakened at an uncivilized hour.
He was irritated at being awakened so early.
He was awakened by a weird and unearthly moaning.
I was awakened by the rumble of a train passing by.
I hate being awakened from a deep sleep by a loud bell.
His annoyance that he had been awakened so early was evident.
Bill slept a little until he was awakened to take his turn on guard.
She was awakened by a noise at two in the morning.
They were awakened to the sad facts.
Her feelings of affection are dormant but easily awakened.
